    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate floor pan fatigue and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing stability. The suspension retains its sharp factory-tuned geometry with crisp turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the chassis remains stiff and the powertrain pulls hard through every gear. A perfect entry point for the purist seeking a visceral, analog M-car experience.",
